## 3rd Party Workflow Email

### Location
* **Admin Console:** Site Manager > System Emails > 3rd Party Workflow Emails
* **SFTP & Develop Mode:** /Layouts/OutboundEmails/Workflow3rdParty.html

### Tags

Tag | Description
-------------- | -------------
`{tag_3rdpartycontent}` |  Content defined in the workflow step to be sent to the recipient
`{tag_emailaddress}` |	Email address of the recipient
`{tag_formsummary}` |	The summary of web form if third-party email being sent with first step of workflow
`{tag_name}` |	Name of item
`{tag_objectid}` |	Item ID
`{tag_recipientname}` |	Full name of the recipient
